COVID19 ICD10CM Value Set for History of Cerebrovascular Accident

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm
    Code Display
    Z86.73 Personal history of transient ischemic attack (TIA), and cerebral infarction without residual deficits
